title: Videohive - After Effects Project Files - Album Love
description:
A stunning display of your images in a sunny grass. This template is ideal for all all occasions family photos and child photos, weddings, anniversaries, birthdays.

Main Features

Available in Full HD (1080p) HD (720p) and SD (480p)
14/26/42 image / video
Every shot have a text
Easy to insert your photos and videos
No plugins required
Includes video tutorial
After Effects CS5 or higher
25 fps
